name: Goblet Workflows
shortDescription: Goblet Workflows is a wrapper around GCP Workflows, which is a fully-managed orchestration platform that executes services in an order that you define: a workflow. These workflows can combine services
longDescription: Goblet Workflows is a wrapper around GCP Workflows, which is a fully-managed orchestration platform that executes services in an order that you define: a workflow. These workflows can combine services
